text: Duygu Aynacı (born June 26, 1996) is a female Turkish weightlifter competing in the 69 kg or 75 kg divisions. Aynacı earned a quota spot for the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1996 births Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Turkish female weightlifters Category:Weightlifters at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic weightlifters of Turkey
